gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 108, Bulls 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Cavaliers defeated the Bulls, 108-105. Donovan Mitchell recorded 30 points, six rebounds and seven assists for the Cavaliers, while Isaac Okoro added 16 points (4-8 3PT FG) in the victory. Coby White tallied a game-high 32 points (5-8 3PT FG), along with seven rebounds and four assists for the Bulls in the losing effort. The Cavaliers improve to 36-17 on the season, while the Bulls fall to 26-29.
